      },
      "date": "2013-02-19 10:03:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\nSorry for the loss of earlier reviews, but seems the way I cherry-picked your patch caused a new version to be created ... Anyway \"--disable-maintainer-mode\" feature/option is now available with this patch and allows us to use it in the configure step of the DKMS rpms (LU-1032).",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "1b9bd35f0ed6a2061393a0754c0be5adc9171102",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 147,
